ActAgricultural Products Marketing Act
SubjectOntario Grain Order
PrecisONTARIO GRAIN ORDER to (1) strengthen and expand the commodity boards’ authority that willl regulate the interprovincial and export trade of their commodity; and (2) allow for the collection of levies in interprovincial and export trade to the same extent as those collected for intraprovincial trade.
